  "title": "Mellow Filipino Toor Dal Curry",
  "description": "A herbal and juicy Filipino dish featuring toor dal, perfect for a lazy Sunday, and is dairy-free friendly. It has a char-grill-yang flavor from the use of grilled onions and garlic.",
